---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="crypto donation wallets"
  description="Accept crypto donations via Monero, Litecoin, Solana, and Bitcoin. Anonymous donations welcome."
>
  <nav style="margin-bottom: 32px;">
    <a href="/" style="color: var(--text-link); font-weight: 600;">← back to home</a>
  </nav>

  <h1>crypto wallets</h1>

  <div class="alert">
    <div class="alert-line">
      <strong>PRIVACY:</strong> all crypto donations are anonymous. I don't see who sent what. Perfect
      for anons.
    </div>
    <div class="alert-line">
      <strong>ANY AMOUNT:</strong> even $1 helps. Crypto fees are usually low, so no minimum.
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2>available wallets</h2>

  <div class="wallet-grid">
    <div class="wallet">
      <span class="wallet-label">MONERO (XMR)</span>
      <div class="wallet-addr">
        87LMfkDhi4vLchGBL4jZU2fUFoDHq6afzZn3jc5ZkMrN5fbs1NZ8VbKEjXecHwu6rZHtXCQpjPZgdEScw9zd3tqmAoVP3Jc
      </div>
      <p style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-xs); margin-top: 8px;">
        ✓ best for anon
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wallet">
      <span class="wallet-label">LITECOIN (LTC)</span>
      <div class="wallet-addr">ltc1q37h3szghljh8f0fjcxkugj8u2lc4zluvzr2jd3</div>
      <p style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-xs); margin-top: 8px;"></p>
    </div>

    <div class="wallet">
      <span class="wallet-label">SOLANA (SOL)</span>
      <div class="wallet-addr">6xzqAPx87JV5cyMmFkxJWEw247FfpCrWS8CSgVe8MoMW</div>
      <p style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-xs); margin-top: 8px;">
        ✓ Near-instant
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="wallet">
      <span class="wallet-label">BITCOIN (BTC)</span>
      <div class="wallet-addr">bc1qml7y5xkacspt38c9fh4p524nqpjkr90dl3vs7a</div>
      <p style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-xs); margin-top: 8px;">
        ⚠ Higher fees
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <h2 id="whycrypto">why crypto?</h2>
  <div class="info-box">
    <ul>
      <li><strong>No middleman fees:</strong> PayPal takes 5-10% and I'm stingy.</li>
      <li>
        <strong>no content censorship:</strong> using kofi and paypal, i need to make sure my public work
        is nothing too crazy.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <h2>how to send</h2>
  <div class="accordion">
    <details class="accordion-item">
      <summary class="accordion-summary">I've never used crypto before. Is it hard?</summary>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <p style="margin-bottom: 12px;">Not really. Here's the simple version:</p>
        <ol style="margin-left: 24px; color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li>Download a crypto wallet app (like CoinLayout, Kraken, or Exodus)</li>
          <li>Buy some crypto with your card/bank</li>
          <li>Copy one of my wallet addresses above</li>
          <li>Send the amount you want</li>
        </ol>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-sm);">
          Do be careful since all coins is different.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="accordion-item">
      <summary class="accordion-summary">Which crypto should I use?</summary>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <p><strong>For anonymity:</strong> Monero (XMR) - completely private transactions</p>
        <p><strong>For speed & low fees:</strong> Litecoin (LTC) or Solana (SOL)</p>
        <p><strong>For simplicity:</strong> Bitcoin (BTC) - easiest to buy, but higher fees</p>
        <p style="margin-top: 12px; color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-sm);">
          Honestly, use whatever you already have. I can accept all of them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>

    <details class="accordion-item">
      <summary class="accordion-summary">How do I know you received my donation?</summary>
      <div class="accordion-content">
        <p>
          Crypto transactions are public (except Monero). You can verify on blockchain explorers:
        </p>
        <ul style="margin: 12px 0 12px 24px; color: var(--text-secondary);">
          <li>Bitcoin: blockchain.com</li>
          <li>Litecoin: blockchair.com</li>
          <li>Solana: solscan.io</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-sm);">
          I also update the progress bar on the homepage when I receive donations.
        </p>
      </div>
    </details>
  </div>

  <div class="info-box">
    <p style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 8px;">prefer traditional payment?</p>
    <p style="color: var(--text-secondary);">
      Ko-fi (PayPal/Card): <a href="https://ko-fi.com/homelessqueen">link here</a>
    </p>
    <p style="margin-top: 8px; color: var(--text-tertiary); font-size: var(--font-size-sm);">
      Note: PayPal has higher fees and worse conversion rates for me, but it works if crypto isn't
      your thing.
    </p>
  </div>
</Layout>
